00:17:43.696 --> 00:17:44.746 A:middle
when VoiceOver is running.

00:17:45.226 --> 00:17:47.066 A:middle
Let's go ahead and see.

00:17:47.066 --> 00:17:48.006 A:middle
&gt;&gt; VOICEOVER: Make sandwich.

